<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śubhamastu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> svasti śrī śakābdaṁ 1593 yiṁddumīṁda cellēṭi virōdhikṛtu saṁvatsaraṁ phālguṇa śu 13 bhṛguvāraṁnāḍu makhā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>nakṣatraṁ kūḍina yī śubhadinamaṁdu dakṣiṇapugaṭuna pāṁḍikulāśini vaḷanāḍu nityōtsava vīdhi vaḷanāḍu tiruvaraṁgaṁ tirupati
<lb n="3"/>perumāḷlu śrīraṁganāthasvāmi śrībhaṁḍārānaku śrīmatu viśvanāthanāyani cokkanāthanāyanayyavāri kaiṁkaryaṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/>vuṁḍḍēcōṭi Aḷagādrināyani pautṛḍu kā <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> panāyani putṛṁḍḍu pradhānicōṭi Aḷagādri sāṣṭāṁganamaskāraṁ samarpiṁci śrīraṁganāya
<lb n="5" break="no"/>kulakovila <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> vrōśiyicina kramaṁ nākaiṁkaryamugānu <gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> rē<unclear>vu</unclear>kāvērikipu <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/><note n="531-1">The rest of the record is badly damaged.</note> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> prākā 
</p>

